00:26:42,440 --> 00:26:43,319
Banner!

879
00:26:45,160 --> 00:26:48,680
(Congratulations to Mr. Yu
on his new car!)

880
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:49,500
♪Rolling in cash♪

881
00:26:49,500 --> 00:26:51,000
(From this day on, he rises to the top.)

882
00:26:51,000 --> 00:26:51,880
♪Rolling in cash♪

883
00:26:52,680 --> 00:26:54,360
♪Rolling in cash♪

884
00:26:55,480 --> 00:26:56,000
Fantastic!

885
00:27:03,520 --> 00:27:06,559
King oyster, oyster,

886
00:27:06,599 --> 00:27:08,359
shiitake, and white beech mushrooms

887
00:27:08,559 --> 00:27:09,559
are all the soul of the dish.

888
00:27:10,119 --> 00:27:11,839
When the water boils,

889
00:27:11,879 --> 00:27:13,839
add peppercorns and ginger.

890
00:27:14,200 --> 00:27:15,760
Then simmer on low heat.

891
00:27:16,359 --> 00:27:17,520
Got it.

892
00:27:28,000 --> 00:27:28,879
You scared me.

893
00:27:29,159 --> 00:27:29,879
What are you doing here?

894
00:27:29,879 --> 00:27:30,280
Yitong.

895
00:27:30,440 --> 00:27:31,440
You really kept this quiet.

896
00:27:31,599 --> 00:27:32,319
Such huge news,

897
00:27:32,359 --> 00:27:33,720
and you didn't show a thing.

898
00:27:33,920 --> 00:27:34,399
No wonder.

899
00:27:34,399 --> 00:27:35,599
One day you were serving people,

900
00:27:35,599 --> 00:27:36,599
the next, they served you.

901
00:27:36,799 --> 00:27:37,760
Now, it all makes sense.

902
00:27:37,960 --> 00:27:39,440
I am the fool.

903
00:27:39,599 --> 00:27:40,119
Anyway,

904
00:27:40,159 --> 00:27:41,399
congratulations.

905
00:27:41,399 --> 00:27:42,240
Get to the point.

906
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:43,280
Say what you came to say.

907
00:27:43,480 --> 00:27:44,159
Look at you.

908
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,359
Always straight to the point.

909
00:27:45,520 --> 00:27:46,559
Fine. I will be direct.

910
00:27:46,839 --> 00:27:48,119
I came to see my investor.

911
00:27:49,480 --> 00:27:50,359
What investor?

912
00:27:50,480 --> 00:27:51,040
I know

913
00:27:51,119 --> 00:27:52,280
you're a normal university grad.

914
00:27:52,359 --> 00:27:52,879
I also know

915
00:27:53,040 --> 00:27:54,000
you work at a travel agency

916
00:27:54,040 --> 00:27:55,040
and do tutoring on the side.

917
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:56,280
So,

918
00:27:56,440 --> 00:27:57,839
why keep doing odd jobs?

919
00:27:57,920 --> 00:27:59,720
Let us partner up

920
00:27:59,879 --> 00:28:01,720
and move into education together.

921
00:28:01,879 --> 00:28:02,920
I have prepared the materials.

922
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:03,920
That sounds terrifying.

923
00:28:04,559 --> 00:28:05,760
You are not interested?

924
00:28:06,639 --> 00:28:07,359
I am.

925
00:28:07,960 --> 00:28:08,760
If you are...

926
00:28:08,760 --> 00:28:09,520
I'm interested

927
00:28:09,520 --> 00:28:10,799
in any project without you.

928
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:11,720
Go home.

929
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:12,559
Don't waste your time.

930
00:28:14,480 --> 00:28:15,920
What's so great about it?

931
00:28:15,920 --> 00:28:17,040
So you got rich overnight.

932
00:28:17,159 --> 00:28:17,839
Whether you can handle

933
00:28:17,839 --> 00:28:18,559
this sudden fortune

934
00:28:18,599 --> 00:28:19,399
is another matter.

935
00:28:21,520 --> 00:28:22,040
Mom.

936
00:28:22,799 --> 00:28:23,480
Hey, Yitong.

937
00:28:28,280 --> 00:28:29,799
Master, you are back.

938
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:32,280
What are you doing here?

939
00:28:32,839 --> 00:28:33,399
What is this?

940
00:28:33,639 --> 00:28:34,680
I was just helping...

941
00:28:34,680 --> 00:28:35,319
Helping what?

942
00:28:35,359 --> 00:28:36,559
Ambition is not used like this.

943
00:28:36,720 --> 00:28:38,000
This is getting ugly.

944
00:28:38,000 --> 00:28:38,520
Go home.

945
00:28:38,879 --> 00:28:39,319
Master.

946
00:28:39,319 --> 00:28:39,839
Just leave.

947
00:28:40,000 --> 00:28:40,559
Stay out of it.

948
00:28:40,559 --> 00:28:41,520
This has nothing to do with you.

949
00:28:41,559 --> 00:28:42,200
Leave.

950
00:28:42,879 --> 00:28:43,839
Master.

951
00:28:44,200 --> 00:28:44,639
Hurry.

952
00:28:44,760 --> 00:28:46,280
Master. What are you doing?

953
00:28:46,520 --> 00:28:47,480
I only came

954
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:48,200
to visit you and your mom.

955
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:49,280
I mentored you for so long.

956
00:28:49,319 --> 00:28:49,960
I never knew

957
00:28:49,960 --> 00:28:51,159
you wanted to visit us before.

958
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:51,839
Why are all of you

959
00:28:51,839 --> 00:28:52,639
so hard to get rid of?

960
00:28:52,639 --> 00:28:53,520
Take your things,

961
00:28:53,599 --> 00:28:54,639
turn left out that door,

962
00:28:54,639 --> 00:28:55,799
leave, and go back to your home.

963
00:28:55,799 --> 00:28:56,480
Now. Hurry.

964
00:29:13,480 --> 00:29:14,079
Ma'am.

965
00:29:14,520 --> 00:29:15,720
I will visit you another time.

966
00:29:15,920 --> 00:29:16,559
All right.

967
00:29:18,559 --> 00:29:19,240
Put your thoughts

968
00:29:19,240 --> 00:29:20,520
toward something useful.

969
00:29:20,960 --> 00:29:21,960
You're a waste of space.

970
00:29:25,079 --> 00:29:26,359
You let just anyone in here.

971
00:29:26,359 --> 00:29:27,280
You should have called me

972
00:29:27,319 --> 00:29:28,200
when she came to our home.

973
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,000
Nice car. Look.

974
00:29:37,359 --> 00:29:38,480
That is a fine car.

975
00:29:38,520 --> 00:29:39,280
Over a million.

976
00:29:39,359 --> 00:29:39,639
Isn't...?

977
00:29:39,639 --> 00:29:40,079
What?

978
00:29:40,159 --> 00:29:41,159
Isn't that Yu?

979
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:42,119
Wasn't he dirt poor?

980
00:29:42,119 --> 00:29:42,520
Right.

981
00:29:42,520 --> 00:29:43,720
He won 130 million.

982
00:29:43,720 --> 00:29:44,359
Him?

983
00:29:44,599 --> 00:29:45,639
Unbelievable, right?

984
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:47,040
Mr. Yu.

985
00:29:47,040 --> 00:29:47,839
Isn't this your car?

986
00:29:47,879 --> 00:29:48,559
Wealth suits you.

987
00:29:48,639 --> 00:29:49,359
Let me borrow some luck.

988
00:29:51,000 --> 00:29:51,720
Mind your manners.

989
00:29:52,159 --> 00:29:52,920
He is rich now.

990
00:29:52,920 --> 00:29:54,200
Hi, Mr. Yu, I'm Lin Ying's mother.

991
00:29:54,559 --> 00:29:55,799
Here is my card.

992
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:57,200
Come by my company sometime.

993
00:29:57,319 --> 00:29:58,399
We have excellent projects.

994
00:29:58,680 --> 00:30:00,040
I hope we can work together.

995
00:30:00,480 --> 00:30:01,559
Mr. Yu in a luxury car.

996
00:30:01,559 --> 00:30:03,440
A fine car for a fine man.

997
00:30:03,520 --> 00:30:05,000
What a perfect match!

998
00:30:05,159 --> 00:30:06,319
Do not call me Mr. Wu anymore.

999
00:30:06,440 --> 00:30:07,200
Call me the matchmaker.

1000
00:30:08,159 --> 00:30:09,119
So that is it.

1001
00:30:09,639 --> 00:30:10,440
There are not many cars

1002
00:30:10,559 --> 00:30:11,319
like this around here.

1003
00:30:11,440 --> 00:30:13,359
Mr. Yu looks powerful in it.

1004
00:30:13,359 --> 00:30:13,920
This is the only one.

1005
00:30:14,159 --> 00:30:15,399
No wonder Mr. Yu

1006
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:17,240
has been so blessed lately.

1007
00:30:17,599 --> 00:30:20,119
Turns out he's the God of Wealth.

1008
00:30:22,240 --> 00:30:23,399
Are you in the car club?

1009
00:30:23,879 --> 00:30:25,119
Let us hang out sometime.

1010
00:30:25,240 --> 00:30:26,639
Why sometime? Let us go now.

1011
00:30:26,760 --> 00:30:27,280
Sure.

1012
00:30:27,480 --> 00:30:28,280
Yes. Absolutely.

1013
00:30:29,040 --> 00:30:29,839
Isn't that your dad?

1014
00:30:31,680 --> 00:30:32,559
Why is your dad

1015
00:30:32,599 --> 00:30:32,920
with my dad?

1016
00:30:32,920 --> 00:30:33,359
No idea.

1017
00:30:34,240 --> 00:30:35,520
Mr. Yu got a new car.

1018
00:30:35,799 --> 00:30:36,960
Any chance you might

1019
00:30:36,960 --> 00:30:37,760
upgrade your house too?

1020
00:30:38,280 --> 00:30:39,319
Move to Haicang Bay.

1021
00:30:39,639 --> 00:30:40,480
We can be neighbors.

1022
00:30:40,480 --> 00:30:42,200
Haicang Bay? I live there too.

1023
00:30:42,559 --> 00:30:43,440
Let us add each other.

1024
00:30:43,639 --> 00:30:44,480
Stay in touch.

1025
00:30:44,680 --> 00:30:45,960
Why later? Let us do it now.

1026
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:47,399
Group chat, everyone.

1027
00:30:47,639 --> 00:30:49,079
Let us make one now.

1028
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:50,680
How about a photo?

1029
00:30:50,799 --> 00:30:52,200
- Sure.
- Come on.

1030
00:30:52,359 --> 00:30:52,680
Let's do it.

1031
00:30:52,680 --> 00:30:53,119
Over here.

1032
00:30:53,119 --> 00:30:54,319
Get the car in the shot.

1033
00:30:54,520 --> 00:30:55,879
- All right.
- Here we go.

1034
00:30:56,839 --> 00:30:58,040
- This way.
- Get the car in the shot.

1035
00:30:58,159 --> 00:30:58,599
The car.

1036
00:30:58,799 --> 00:30:59,559
Mr. Yu.

1037
00:30:59,879 --> 00:31:00,559
Cheese!

1038
00:31:00,720 --> 00:31:01,000
Okay.

1039
00:31:01,879 --> 00:31:02,520
Great.

1040
00:31:02,520 --> 00:31:02,839
Cool.

1041
00:31:03,599 --> 00:31:04,799
Let us meet often.

1042
00:31:04,879 --> 00:31:05,359
Sure.

1043
00:31:05,399 --> 00:31:06,200
Keep in touch.

1044
00:31:12,040 --> 00:31:13,399
Was this your dad's idea?

1045
00:31:13,799 --> 00:31:14,960
Making my dad embarrass himself?

1046
00:31:23,639 --> 00:31:24,520
I thought

1047
00:31:24,520 --> 00:31:25,680
you would have changed your backpack.

1048
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:26,639
Your family

1049
00:31:26,639 --> 00:31:27,599
is so rich now.

1050
00:31:28,319 --> 00:31:28,760
Right?

1051
00:31:30,240 --> 00:31:31,760
You know where this backpack came from?

1052
00:31:33,240 --> 00:31:34,119
I volunteered

1053
00:31:34,440 --> 00:31:35,760
and gave haircuts

1054
00:31:35,760 --> 00:31:36,799
to blind elders.

1055
00:31:37,200 --> 00:31:38,000
They could not see,

1056
00:31:38,079 --> 00:31:39,040
but they all said I did well.

1057
00:31:39,599 --> 00:31:40,960
I cut eight people's hair in one day.

1058
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:42,599
They pooled their money,
five or ten yuan,

1059
00:31:42,599 --> 00:31:43,680
and bought me this backpack.

1060
00:31:44,119 --> 00:31:45,359
So it is priceless.

1061
00:31:47,440 --> 00:31:48,760
May I take a look?

1062
00:31:56,720 --> 00:31:58,040
Mr. Yu, I'm leaving.

1063
00:31:58,119 --> 00:31:59,159
Let us play ball sometime.

1064
00:32:07,920 --> 00:32:09,240
It feels like

1065
00:32:09,639 --> 00:32:11,440
we are the only parents left.

1066
00:32:12,040 --> 00:32:13,399
Could people be after you

1067
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:14,480
because of that 100 million?

1068
00:32:17,480 --> 00:32:19,119
♪Work hard and make money♪

1069
00:32:19,319 --> 00:32:20,559
♪I want to get rich♪

1070
00:32:20,559 --> 00:32:21,140
(Unknown number)

1071
00:32:21,599 --> 00:32:22,440
It's my son.

1072
00:32:22,720 --> 00:32:23,440
Answer it. Hurry.

1073
00:32:24,480 --> 00:32:24,960
Hello?

1074
00:32:25,159 --> 00:32:26,240
Dad?

1075
00:32:27,040 --> 00:32:27,799
Where are you?

1076
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:29,920
Behind you. On the footbridge.

1077
00:32:31,040 --> 00:32:31,639
What are you doing?

1078
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,359
Come pick me up across the street.

1079
00:32:37,920 --> 00:32:38,480
What does that mean?

1080
00:32:57,559 --> 00:32:58,359
Bye, Wenwen.

1081
00:32:58,520 --> 00:32:59,000
Bye.

1082
00:33:02,559 --> 00:33:03,960
What are you doing?

1083
00:33:04,040 --> 00:33:04,879
Why did you make me

1084
00:33:04,879 --> 00:33:06,200
drive across the street?

1085
00:33:06,520 --> 00:33:07,159
It's embarrassing.

1086
00:33:09,520 --> 00:33:10,399
I got a new car

1087
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:12,319
to give you some dignity.

1088
00:33:12,319 --> 00:33:13,399
How is it embarrassing?

1089
00:33:13,680 --> 00:33:15,040
A new car gives me dignity?

1090
00:33:18,190 --> 00:33:21,070
(Bridgeway Financial)

1091
00:33:21,119 --> 00:33:21,839
(Bridgeway Financial)
Si,

1092
00:33:22,680 --> 00:33:23,359
I am going up.

1093
00:33:24,319 --> 00:33:25,119
You and the others

1094
00:33:25,119 --> 00:33:26,680
stay in the car.

1095
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:28,760
It's fine.

1096
00:33:28,920 --> 00:33:29,639
Nothing serious.

1097
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:31,639
Unless I call you,

1098
00:33:31,639 --> 00:33:32,559
no one comes up.

1099
00:33:33,639 --> 00:33:34,079
Okay.

1100
00:33:36,319 --> 00:33:36,879
Who are you?

1101
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:43,639
Who is in charge here?

1102
00:33:44,639 --> 00:33:45,559
Who are you looking for?

1103
00:33:46,040 --> 00:33:48,480
I asked who is in charge here.

1104
00:33:48,520 --> 00:33:48,960
I am.

1105
00:33:49,240 --> 00:33:50,119
What do you want?

1106
00:34:06,159 --> 00:34:07,319
You're in charge, right?

1107
00:34:09,320 --> 00:34:10,960
There is 900,000 in this bag.

1108
00:34:11,639 --> 00:34:12,239
Yu Ming.

1109
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:14,199
Do you know him?

1110
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,400
He borrowed 800,000, owes 900,000,

1111
00:34:16,559 --> 00:34:17,520
and mortgaged a small apartment.

1112
00:34:18,199 --> 00:34:18,719
Yes.

1113
00:34:19,239 --> 00:34:19,920
That is him.

1114
00:34:22,559 --> 00:34:23,920
The money he owes you,

1115
00:34:24,679 --> 00:34:25,679
I will pay it for him.

1116
00:34:26,119 --> 00:34:26,880
From now on,

1117
00:34:26,920 --> 00:34:28,320
none of you should bother him.

1118
00:34:40,679 --> 00:34:41,360
Hello?

1119
00:34:43,159 --> 00:34:43,920
Si.

1120
00:34:44,759 --> 00:34:45,360
I'm fine.

1121
00:34:46,159 --> 00:34:47,320
Everything is under control.

1122
00:34:48,119 --> 00:34:50,000
There are only four or five of them.

1123
00:34:50,119 --> 00:34:50,440
It's fine.

1124
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:51,559
I can handle this myself.

1125
00:34:52,800 --> 00:34:53,520
Don't come up.

1126
00:34:53,599 --> 00:34:54,559
What would you come up for?

1127
00:34:55,040 --> 00:34:55,599
Du.

1128
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,480
900,000. Correct.

1129
00:34:57,960 --> 00:34:58,440
Stay put.

1130
00:35:03,759 --> 00:35:04,719
Give him back the deed.

1131
00:35:07,440 --> 00:35:07,880
Small matter.

1132
00:35:08,639 --> 00:35:09,079
Nothing at all.

1133
00:35:10,360 --> 00:35:10,639
Good.

1134
00:35:20,079 --> 00:35:20,599
Clean and simple.

1135
00:35:22,040 --> 00:35:23,440
All right. My business is done.

1136
00:35:23,920 --> 00:35:24,639
I'm very busy.

1137
00:35:30,960 --> 00:35:31,520
I'm leaving.

1138
00:35:32,480 --> 00:35:33,119
I have things to do.

1139
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:46,079
Integrity is gold. Trust is a bridge.

1140
00:35:46,920 --> 00:35:47,679
When in need,

1141
00:35:48,679 --> 00:35:49,559
come to Bridgeway.

1142
00:35:58,320 --> 00:36:01,400
Congratulations to Mr. Yu
on his jackpot!

1143
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:07,040
Everybody up!

1144
00:36:10,159 --> 00:36:11,159
Our VIPs over there,

1145
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:13,159
dance!

1146
00:36:14,960 --> 00:36:16,679
Let's party!

1147
00:36:18,239 --> 00:36:19,559
No more. No more.

1148
00:36:19,599 --> 00:36:21,079
Sit down.

1149
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:28,199
Let me tell you.

1150
00:36:28,759 --> 00:36:30,279
Brothers, cousins,

1151
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:32,320
now they all butter me up.

1152
00:36:33,480 --> 00:36:34,639
Qian Weijie

1153
00:36:34,719 --> 00:36:36,119
came to my home,

1154
00:36:36,119 --> 00:36:37,719
grinning from ear to ear,

1155
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:39,040
like a begging dog.

1156
00:36:39,320 --> 00:36:40,880
I finally feel confident.

1157
00:36:42,239 --> 00:36:43,960
Bro, we're out of booze. Stop drinking.

1158
00:36:44,119 --> 00:36:45,079
We're out?

1159
00:36:45,800 --> 00:36:48,400
I can buy more!

1160
00:39:39,079 --> 00:39:39,960
Why are you sleeping here?

1161
00:39:42,239 --> 00:39:43,320
Yu Ming?

1162
00:39:44,759 --> 00:39:45,759
How did you end up here?

1163
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:47,239
How much did you drink?

1164
00:39:47,239 --> 00:39:48,440
You are sleeping on the street.

1165
00:39:48,759 --> 00:39:50,239
Have you no shame?

1166
00:39:50,679 --> 00:39:52,079
Bigfoot.

1167
00:39:52,520 --> 00:39:53,279
Can you get up?

1168
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:54,400
I can.

1169
00:39:55,480 --> 00:39:56,520
Pull me up.

1170
00:39:57,960 --> 00:39:58,800
Well, now,

1171
00:39:58,800 --> 00:40:00,000
you are a public safety risk.

1172
00:40:00,040 --> 00:40:00,559
I'm telling you.

1173
00:40:00,559 --> 00:40:02,079
You are amazing. Truly.

1174
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:04,440
Even like this, you still found me.

1175
00:40:04,559 --> 00:40:05,599
I'm off work,

1176
00:40:05,599 --> 00:40:06,520
and now I'm your driver.

1177
00:40:06,559 --> 00:40:07,360
I must owe you big-time.

1178
00:40:08,360 --> 00:40:08,880
Get in.

1179
00:40:18,520 --> 00:40:19,239
You're not that drunk.

1180
00:40:19,279 --> 00:40:20,520
You still remember to buckle up.

1181
00:40:27,119 --> 00:40:28,040
I heard

1182
00:40:28,040 --> 00:40:28,840
you won the lottery.

1183
00:40:29,279 --> 00:40:30,599
Didn't know you had that luck.

1184
00:40:31,440 --> 00:40:32,880
You've got money now. Great.

1185
00:40:33,000 --> 00:40:34,000
Have a drink to celebrate, fine.

1186
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:35,279
But look at you.

1187
00:40:35,719 --> 00:40:36,719
When your wife sees this,

1188
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:37,639
she will scold you.

1189
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:41,199
Listen,

1190
00:40:41,360 --> 00:40:42,719
even if you are rich, don't show off.

1191
00:40:42,960 --> 00:40:44,480
Put it into real assets.

1192
00:40:44,639 --> 00:40:45,440
Buy property.

1193
00:40:46,040 --> 00:40:47,159
Replace that shabby apartment

1194
00:40:47,199 --> 00:40:47,480
of yours.

1195
00:40:47,559 --> 00:40:48,079
Get a bigger one.

1196
00:40:48,759 --> 00:40:50,279
Once Wenwen and your wife are happy,

1197
00:40:50,520 --> 00:40:51,719
your life gets easier.

1198
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:53,599
I am talking to you.

1199
00:40:53,639 --> 00:40:54,400
Are you listening?

1200
00:40:54,520 --> 00:40:55,320
I am listening.

1201
00:40:58,960 --> 00:40:59,840
Up ahead.

1202
00:41:00,639 --> 00:41:01,639
Turn right.

1203
00:41:02,239 --> 00:41:02,960
Turn right?

1204
00:41:04,159 --> 00:41:05,239
This is not your home.

1205
00:41:13,119 --> 00:41:14,440
Good. All right, here.

1206
00:41:15,360 --> 00:41:16,239
This is it.

1207
00:41:24,040 --> 00:41:24,800
Where is this?

1208
00:41:25,759 --> 00:41:26,599
My home.

1209
00:41:27,639 --> 00:41:28,279
Your home?

1210
00:41:28,480 --> 00:41:29,079
You bought it?

1211
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:30,800
Of course.

1212
00:41:30,880 --> 00:41:31,880
You thought I stole it?

1213
00:41:36,199 --> 00:41:37,599
Your driving is not great.

1214
00:41:37,599 --> 00:41:38,920
That last jolt said it all.

1215
00:41:43,440 --> 00:41:43,920
See?

1216
00:41:48,040 --> 00:41:48,960
Is this my place or not?

1217
00:41:50,880 --> 00:41:51,440
Showing off.

1218
00:41:54,679 --> 00:41:56,159
Watch your step on the stairs.

1219
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:58,440
You call this a home?

1220
00:41:58,679 --> 00:42:00,119
Who could live in this dump?

1221
00:42:00,719 --> 00:42:01,759
Well,

1222
00:42:02,759 --> 00:42:05,400
I just wanted one last taste

1223
00:42:05,400 --> 00:42:06,800
of having nothing.

1224
00:42:06,960 --> 00:42:09,480
Soon, this place

1225
00:42:09,520 --> 00:42:10,920
will be magnificent.

1226
00:42:15,480 --> 00:42:16,360
Look at you, all smug.

1227
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:17,599
The world isn't big enough for you.

1228
00:43:05,080 --> 00:43:07,880
(Next Episode)

1229
00:43:08,279 --> 00:43:09,159
(Actor, Gu Jiacheng)
I'm Gu Jiacheng.

1230
00:43:09,159 --> 00:43:11,159
(Actor, Gu Jiacheng)
I invite you to watch Wonder Wall.

1231
00:43:11,520 --> 00:43:11,840
Turn.

1232
00:43:12,159 --> 00:43:13,239
Turn. Yeah, yeah, yeah.

1233
00:43:13,279 --> 00:43:14,000
Stop, stop, stop.

1234
00:43:14,199 --> 00:43:15,360
Right here. Dig upward.

1235
00:43:15,440 --> 00:43:16,320
I'm telling you, this is it.

1236
00:43:16,520 --> 00:43:17,360
We were off.

1237
00:43:17,639 --> 00:43:18,639
You've got a lot of trash at your place.

1238
00:43:18,840 --> 00:43:19,960
Alright, alright.

1239
00:43:20,000 --> 00:43:20,400
Thanks. Thanks.

1240
00:43:20,400 --> 00:43:21,320
Where's this being hauled to?

1241
00:43:21,480 --> 00:43:22,079
The dump.

1242
00:43:23,360 --> 00:43:24,119
Twelve bags

1243
00:43:24,239 --> 00:43:24,920
that big?

1244
00:43:25,040 --> 00:43:25,759
It's definitely the money.

1245
00:43:25,880 --> 00:43:27,719
I started with nothing

1246
00:43:27,920 --> 00:43:29,360
to owning a luxury villa.

1247
00:43:29,360 --> 00:43:31,040
As long as you've got
courage, you succeed.

1248
00:43:31,159 --> 00:43:31,599
Exactly.

1249
00:43:32,599 --> 00:43:34,480
Let's drink to that.

1250
00:43:35,159 --> 00:43:35,759
Ming,

1251
00:43:35,759 --> 00:43:37,040
look at the state you're in.

1252
00:43:55,610 --> 00:44:02,620
♪The road ahead is still so long
Where have you gone?♪

1253
00:44:04,180 --> 00:44:11,340
♪Under the blazing sun
I keep heading north♪

1254
00:44:12,760 --> 00:44:20,220
♪To those who pass me by
You don't have to look at me♪

1255
00:44:21,360 --> 00:44:28,640
♪Just keep walking your own way
I'll manage on my own♪

1256
00:44:31,630 --> 00:44:35,230
♪Is the rain falling hard?♪

1257
00:44:35,870 --> 00:44:39,000
♪Is there someone
to hold an umbrella for you?♪

1258
00:44:40,160 --> 00:44:44,940
♪The wind has blown
the numbers off the signs♪

1259
00:44:44,940 --> 00:44:47,930
♪Where am I supposed to go?♪

1260
00:44:48,730 --> 00:44:52,250
♪Can I change my mind?♪

1261
00:44:53,010 --> 00:44:56,240
♪How do I go on without you?♪

1262
00:44:57,550 --> 00:45:02,080
♪When will this
endless rain finally stop?♪

1263
00:45:02,080 --> 00:45:04,780
♪Then I'll wait for you♪

1264
00:45:04,780 --> 00:45:08,780
♪Please don't leave me waiting♪

